sentences.sentence: In the new age Chinese literature there was once a period when linguistic phenomenon of using supernormal grammar prevailed.
sentences.translation: 中国新时期文学，在文学语言上一度出现了大量语法上超常规的语言运用现象。

sentences.sentence: Solid particle erosion (SPE) is very critical on the life cycle of control stage nozzle for supernormal parameters steam turbine.
sentences.translation: 固体颗粒冲蚀严重影响超常参数汽轮机调节级喷嘴寿命。

sentences.sentence: These often affect the physical abilities of the templar endowing a knight with supernormal strength speed defenses or fighting agility.
sentences.translation: 这些技能可以影响到圣堂武士的物理性，赋予骑士超凡的力量、速度、防御或者战斗能力。
